<item>
            <title>[LU-18435] replay of pfl layout resets layout generation</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18435</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;when layout creation (open/create) is being replayed it resets layout generation to 0 and this later prevent layout refresh on the client side as the client wants the layout to increase update an update.&lt;br/&gt;
this way the client can get into a loop trying to refresh a layout. in write(2) this repeats 1000 times and then the write gives up returning 0 bytes written.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
